WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.334
Return of the Ancients adds challenges for the

00:00:01.334 --> 00:00:05.672
first time in a Path of Exile 2 league. You


00:00:05.672 --> 00:00:07.574


00:00:07.574 --> 00:00:10.193
can earn pieces of the Alder Knight armor set for every two challenges you complete,

00:00:10.193 --> 00:00:11.795
so it's worth giving them a try. To check your

00:00:12.362 --> 00:00:15.148
challenge progress and the
requirements to complete them,

00:00:15.148 --> 00:00:17.801
press the H button to open the challenges screen. There

00:00:17.951 --> 00:00:19.319
are a total of eight challenges, ranging from

00:00:19.319 --> 00:00:22.222
easy to quite difficult.

00:00:22.222 --> 00:00:23.923
To complete Rune Seeker, you need to find remnants with

00:00:23.923 --> 00:00:26.626
more slots and craft

00:00:26.626 --> 00:00:28.595
items. Crafting

00:00:29.229 --> 00:00:32.999
seven slots is a fairly difficult challenge,
featuring six waves of enemies. You will need considerable skill to

00:00:32.999 --> 00:00:36.002
take on this battle. There are


00:00:38.638 --> 00:00:39.639


00:00:39.639 --> 00:00:41.408
several optional bosses throughout the campaign.

00:00:41.408 --> 00:00:42.959
To complete Hunter's challenges, you need to

00:00:42.959 --> 00:00:45.361
hunt six of them. The

00:00:45.361 --> 00:00:49.282
last two, The Last Strike, Acti and the
Sandworm, Anandor, can be

00:00:49.282 --> 00:00:51.551
difficult to find in Kali's Crossing. To

00:00:52.185 --> 00:00:55.271
track these bosses,
follow them along the dried-up riverbed, eventually reaching the

00:00:55.388 --> 00:00:57.073
arena.

00:00:58.558 --> 00:01:00.877
Ascendant's challenges


00:01:00.877 --> 00:01:03.880
require you to earn all eight points in the Ascendancy class by completing the Ascendancy Trials.

00:01:03.880 --> 00:01:06.766
Earning the last point can be quite challenging.  You need to

00:01:06.766 --> 00:01:10.220
either defeat Zarok in the fourth level of the Trials of Sekema, or

00:01:10.653 --> 00:01:14.390
find all three keys in the Trials of Chaos and defeat the Trial Master. Of

00:01:15.141 --> 00:01:16.960
these two, the Trials of Chaos will take a very long time as you will need to

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:20.029
run through the trial multiple times. However, the


00:01:20.029 --> 00:01:22.549
Trials of Sekema are more difficult.

00:01:22.549 --> 00:01:25.151
So you must decide which path to take.


00:01:26.719 --> 00:01:28.138
Relicual is simple; you just need to

00:01:28.138 --> 00:01:30.573
identify 50 different types of unique items. Having

00:01:32.025 --> 00:01:33.910
trouble finding unique items?

00:01:33.910 --> 00:01:37.647
Atlas Master Jad has many abilities specializing in discovering unique items.


00:01:39.749 --> 00:01:41.151
To complete Artisan, you will

00:01:41.151 --> 00:01:43.720
need to use multiple different types of crafting items, all

00:01:43.720 --> 00:01:45.839
of which can be obtained in Remnant Encounters.

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:48.441
To complete Cartographer, you will

00:01:48.441 --> 00:01:50.894
need to fully allocate the entire Atlas tree,

00:01:51.177 --> 00:01:52.712
all 300 nodes. You can complete it by

00:01:53.163 --> 00:01:56.883
completing all the maps within the fortress, although this will take
time. There are

00:01:56.916 --> 00:01:58.918
other ways as well. Each time you

00:01:58.918 --> 00:02:01.054
defeat an Arbiter of Divinity, you can

00:02:01.054 --> 00:02:05.175
automatically complete a large area of ​​the fortress.

00:02:06.676 --> 00:02:09.679
By finding citadels in Atlas, you can
find the keys needed for the challenge.

00:02:09.829 --> 00:02:12.832
Each citadel
emits a glowing beam that can be seen even through the fog. You can complete the entire fortress

00:02:13.032 --> 00:02:16.719
by fighting the boss four times.


00:02:17.871 --> 00:02:21.040
Last but not least, there
is Vanquisher, which you should never miss.

00:02:21.391 --> 00:02:24.010
This challenge requires you to defeat three pinnacle bosses, which will be the

00:02:24.010 --> 00:02:25.478
most difficult battles in the game. These are

00:02:25.979 --> 00:02:27.030
Tangmazu,

00:02:27.030 --> 00:02:28.097
the Bodach,

00:02:28.097 --> 00:02:29.682
and Vessel of Kulemak, which are

00:02:30.083 --> 00:02:34.070
 
pinnacle bosses from Delirium and the Ritual Abyss League, respectively.

00:02:34.070 --> 00:02:37.190
To complete this challenge, you will need to complete three quest lines. The

00:02:37.674 --> 00:02:39.909
important thing about the Kula Mak Vessel fight is that you

00:02:39.909 --> 00:02:42.162
need to defeat the fully powered version. You will need to

00:02:42.162 --> 00:02:44.113


00:02:44.113 --> 00:02:46.716
return the fingers during the boss fight, risking not getting any items, and
somehow defeat the boss. As I

00:02:49.352 --> 00:02:50.303
mentioned before, you will receive a piece of

00:02:50.303 --> 00:02:53.223
armor set for every two challenges you complete. You do not


00:02:53.223 --> 00:02:55.675
 
need to complete all the challenges to get some of the rewards,

00:02:55.675 --> 00:02:58.628
but if you do complete all the challenges, you
can show off your skills, as it will be displayed to

00:02:58.778 --> 00:03:02.715
everyone in global chat or on the forums as to how many
challenges you have completed.

00:03:03.149 --> 00:03:05.835
In addition, you will be able to decorate your hideout with this totem ornament, so

00:03:05.835 --> 00:03:07.837
anyone who visits your hideout to trade with you will see that

00:03:07.837 --> 00:03:10.840
you have joined and conquered the league. Try taking on


00:03:11.191 --> 00:03:15.361
 
these challenges in Return of the Ancients on May 30th JST.

00:03:15.562 --> 00:03:17.463
Thanks for watching, see you then
!

